divs: Sighting DetailsI was working security , at a local event , i went outside for some air and a smoke, i had seen two bright , what i thought were stars, i paid no mind to it really , and went back inside to continue my work- whilst working - i was posistioned on the deck area, i looked up again and saw only one of what i thought were stars, lots of people had mentioned seeing them, but then dismissed it quickly as there alchohol intake caught up with them . i continued to watch the object which was now pulsating , i was gobsmacked, it then pulsated another couple of times and blinked then it was gone .
